#summary Data types supported by CIF

= Data types supported by CIF =

By default CIF supports the following native data types:
 # IP address
 # FQDN
 # URI
 # CIDR
 # Email address
 # Malware hash (sha1/md5) (_must be enabled in feed config_)
 # UUID (_generally used by the API_)
